{"tid":2426281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"化驗結果滯後 酒店員工播毒3日","createTime":"2021-02-28T03:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T04:07:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"25bf609e5841ea2df0beff6da9389179750a7184","tid":2426281,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:53:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210228/5LFDUPALHREF7CJWBIHUISALWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210228%2F5LFDUPALHREF7CJWBIHUISALWA%2F&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3kx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=64f49578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210228%2F5LFDUPALHREF7CJWBIHUISALWA%2F&h=183ebeda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210228/5LFDUPALHREF7CJWBIHUISALWA/</a><br />\n<br />\n化驗結果滯後 酒店員工播毒3日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ewzh7uvKMQnQ1MGPlrXF976rcyE=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/C5G6JVRCNZEDDBXOPH3YR3ETBI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fewzh7uvKMQnQ1MGPlrXF976rcyE%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FC5G6JVRCNZEDDBXOPH3YR3ETBI.jpg&h=a10d70fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■銅鑼灣柏寧酒店確認一名員工昨初步確診。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府強迫多個行業僱員須完成檢測才可上班，但檢測結果卻往往滯後，導致隱形病患於社區播毒。新增一名酒店員工初步確診，早於24日檢測，但昨日始公佈他傳染期內於三間酒店工作。醫生批評政府強迫市民做檢測同時，未有增加對應的檢測能力，憂慮因延誤確診令疫情大幅反彈。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：採樣站職員不知名潮須檢測<br />\n<br />\n昨日新增約20宗初步確診，當中不少屬源頭不明個案。一名居於柴灣的31歲男子。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n其中柏寧酒店確認昨日才獲衞。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：帶毒飛沫核可飄浮數小時<br />\n<br />\n一名53歲、在居於馬灣珀麗灣6座，於觀塘駿業街中海日升中心38樓工作的女子亦初步確診。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瑪麗醫院助理中招<br />\n<br />\n瑪麗醫院婦產科一名運作助理其同住家人確診，23日被送到檢疫中心。兩日後低燒，昨日測試結果呈陽性。患者22日最後上班，當時檢測結果為陰性。該名員工主要負責運送文件及環境清潔，毋須接觸病人，上班期間有戴外科口罩，沒有病人及職員被列為密切接觸者。院方將安排同一辦公室另外六名員工檢測。<br />\n<br />\n至於確診的個案，除了尖沙嘴K11 MUSEA的名。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n檢測能力滯後，呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局周五承認，有化驗所檢測效率未達標。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ml695CJPXNfwgeFUOkD_B3X2L9c=/479x334/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7522OOM7ZVASTEOULAFZCVSHUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fml695CJPXNfwgeFUOkD_B3X2L9c%3D%2F479x334%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7522OOM7ZVASTEOULAFZCVSHUQ.gif&h=b1d66554&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a9b9b632860873cb61196692bd5c41326d53de0","tid":2426281,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:54:30.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n===<br />\n簽名檔<br />\n<br />\n[戇鳩警報器: 黃世澤 | martin oei | 交加街38號 ] 警世 黃世澤係令大家用唔到BNO移民既始作俑者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2423877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2423877</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bbaaf1ff2a09838bef3e39fdd507de9dae843c7a","tid":2426281,"uid":265318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T04:07:22.000Z","msg":"已經用左一年時間，<br />\n一邊要強制檢驗，<br />\n一邊仍未到capacity<br />\n<br />\n下一波大過第四波的話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}